109
00:11:05,698 --> 00:11:08,979
In the meantime, city events that are held there

110
00:11:10,099 --> 00:11:14,182
are very careful to make sure that the event in and of itself is accessible.

111
00:11:14,343 --> 00:11:17,065
So we know that grass, for instance, is not an accessible surface.

112
