So using MOBI mats or making sure that activities are happening along the path, we focus on that.

113
00:11:24,351 --> 00:11:30,896
And I know that the space itself has become more accessible over time as DCR has given it attention.

114
00:11:31,097 --> 00:11:37,362
But the shell, at this moment, we want to focus on restoring it and then coming up with a plan for ADA accessibility.

115
00:11:38,132 --> 00:11:39,853
Are the Moby mats available now?

116
00:11:40,493 --> 00:11:42,674
