01:53:00,905 --> 01:53:05,526
So my one question relates actually to your next presentation.

1221
01:53:05,686 --> 01:53:20,410
So it says that in the next presentation for the preserve and protect the historical textile pieces that they will not be available for public access and display after the cleaning.

1222
01:53:21,451 --> 01:53:25,932
